{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/catline.png?t=1738562989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help cats get to sleep in this adorable game, with novel mechanics based on nonograms and sliding puzzles. Nekograms is easy to learn but does get challenging!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/Steamtitles_01.png?t=1738562989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cats only sleep on cushions. Complete a level by helping all cats get to sleep.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/Nekograms_Steam_CatsToSleep.gif?t=1738562989\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/Steamtitles_02.png?t=1738562989\" />Earn stars by completing levels in the fewest number of moves. Achieve 3 stars in every level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/Nekograms_Steam_LevelSelect.gif?t=1738562989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/Steamtitles_03.png?t=1738562989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete the game to unlock Endless Mode and ascend through different states of cat consciousness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/Nekograms_Steam_EndlessMode.gif?t=1738562989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.